dct_title_s: Ciudad de Guatemala. Hoja = sheet 3. Series E954.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 10 meter contour interval and spot elevation. Coordinate conversion NAD 83/WGS 84 to NAD 27. Boundary is entirely within the first-order administrative division of the Departamento de Guatemala. Includes index to adjoining sheets and glossary. Verso: Index to streets. "Map information as of 1996". 1998
dct_creator_sm: Instituto Geográfico Nacional "Ingeniero Alfredo Obiols Gómez"

Guatemala City : Instituto Geográfico Nacional de Guatemala, 1998.
Guatemala. Instituto Geografico Nacional "Ingeniero Alfredo Obiols Gomez" ; United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
